    As a reference , these have the same provenance as the ones sold recently on ebay by lharri, most selling for $20-$25.00;if interested, they can be seen under "completed items"  they were affixed to cardboard and acquired in the 1970's, and when removed from the cardboard, thus the paper loss.

   I will be putting together an alphabetical spreadsheet by player as soon as I get these; prices will be in the $19.00 range.

   In addition, I will also be getting in the same shipment 110+ T205's which have nice fronts (vg-ex/ex)and toning on the backs---probably in the similar price range.  

If anyone would like to "pre-request"!! the spreadsheet for either T205's or the T206's (or both), please email me at [url]forazzurri1@aol.com[/url] and I will forward as soon as spreadsheet is finished..
